    "id": "As for the right of your mother, know she carried you where none carries anyone, gave you of her heart's fruit what none gives, and protected you with all her limbs. She cared not if she hungered while feeding you, thirsted while giving you drink, was naked while clothing you, or suffered sun while shading you. She gave up sleep for you and protected you from heat and cold. You cannot thank her except through Allah's help. As for your father's right, know he is your root; without him you would not exist. Whatever pleases you in yourself, know your father is the root of that blessing. So praise Allah and thank Him accordingly. There is no strength save in Allah.",
